  "response_text": "Task Management API Design:\n\n1. **Base URL:** `https://task-management-api.example.com`\n\n2. **Authentication:** JWT (JSON Web Token) for user authentication. The token will be sent in the `Authorization` header with the format `Bearer {token}`.\n\n3. **Endpoints:**\n\n   a. **User Registration:**\n      - **Endpoint:** `/api/auth/register`\n      - **Method:** `POST`\n      - **Data Format:** JSON\n         ```\n         {\n            \"username\": \"string\",\n            \"email\": \"string\",\n            \"password\": \"string\"\n         }\n         ```\n\n   b. **User Login:**\n      - **Endpoint:** `/api/auth/login`\n      - **Method:** `POST`\n      - **Data Format:** JSON\n         ```\n         {\n            \"email\": \"string\",\n            \"password\": \"string\"\n         }\n         ```\n\n   c. **Create Task:**\n      - **Endpoint:** `/api/tasks`\n      - **Method:** `POST`\n      - **Data Format:** JSON\n         ```\n         {\n            \"title\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"string\",\n            \"due_date\": \"YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SS\",\n            \"priority\": \"low\", \"medium\", \"high\"\n         }\n         ```\n\n   d. **Get All Tasks:**\n      - **Endpoint:** `/api/tasks`\n      - **Method:** `GET`\n      - **Query Parameters:**\n         - `status`: `all`, `active`, `completed` (optional)\n         - `priority`: `low`, `medium`, `high` (optional)\n         - `sort_by`: `due_date`, `priority`, `status` (optional)\n         - `sort_order`: `asc`, `desc` (optional)\n         - `limit`: integer (optional)\n         - `offset`: integer (optional)\n\n   e. **Get Single Task:**\n      - **Endpoint:** `/api/tasks/{task_id}`\n      - **Method:** `GET`\n\n   f. **Update Task:**\n      - **Endpoint:** `/api/tasks/{task_id}`\n      - **Method:** `PUT`\n      - **Data Format:** JSON\n         ```\n         {\n            \"title\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"string\",\n            \"due_date\": \"YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SS\",\n            \"priority\": \"low\", \"medium\", \"high\"\n         }\n        ",
